lines.text: I suppose nothing hurts you.
Only pain.
Enough talk!
A fine magician you are! Go back to juggling apples.
My brother's sister's cousin never said anything about bars.
I think we made the merchant angry.
Are you surprised?
But we didn't steal everything he had!
We didn't have time.
Into the boat!
Death to the world.
Life for Valeria.
How do you attract a man? What I mean is, suppose you set your heart on somebody. What would you do to get him?
Grab him! And take him!
Conan! There are six of them against her!
One, two, three... I think you're right.
I need you.
I'm yours!
I go where I feel myself led.
So I've noticed.
Why are they trying to kill us?
Maybe they want to capture us, and torture us to death.
Too late, my friends... , but come... Come anyway.
Could there ever be anyone else?

[Drunk, helping Jenna with throwing his sword up, hits Malik in the head]
Good. Now you're ready to take on anybody!
